<img src="https://notjustok.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_5073.jpg" alt="Phlex Features Charass on Powerful Benediction Song, &#039;Confirm&#039;"/> Phlex Features Charass on Powerful Benediction Song, 'Confirm' Fast-rising star Phlex revives his benediction single titled “Confirm.” The release comes off the positive reception of his EP titled “Undaunted.” The singer, with soulful singing, conveys his yearnings for bliss and blessings from the source. Phlex delivers on the touching record, with Charass Melody lending his Tekno-style vocals to the music. Confirm is set for addition to playlists by hustlers and dreamers who seek divine showers of blessings in their race to succeed. Listen to Confirm and Undaunted EP below. AUDIO DOWNLOAD The post Phlex Features Charass on Powerful Benediction Song, 'Confirm' appeared first on Most Trusted Voice in Music & Afrobeats from Nigeria & Africa | Notjustok. Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.